summary: This song - it’s a Mary J Blige song, actually - and she got up, and she sang this song that I had never heard of before. All of...
caption: This song - it’s a Mary J Blige song, actually - and she got up, and she sang this song that I had never heard of before. All of a sudden I just felt like, I go through that so much, I doubt myself every single day. No matter what happens, I continue to doubt myself, and I think I always will, and I think it’s something I’m always going to struggle with. But this song helped me and helps me moment to moment. I don’t think we can ever hope to fully get over the things that make us insecure, or the voices in our head that say, you can’t do it, you’re not good enough, nobody likes you, you’re not cool, you’re so annoying…
